	<h1 class="title">作为一个文化现象，《美国偶像》要完结了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">James Poniewozik</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-08 10:00:40 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20374/medium/20374.png?1452136970" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


